    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector-grade specimen, meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment and maintained with obsessive attention to detail. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish entirely free of swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections, further enhanced by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather upholstery remains taut and scent-neutral, with no signs of wear or creasing. Every electronic component and driver-assist feature functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is flawless, supported by a folder of exhaustive service records from authorized specialists. It has never been driven in inclement weather and has been kept in a smoke-free, pet-free household. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to acquire a showroom-quality vehicle that drives exactly as it did on day one.",
